# install
tiffanybot.py requires SQLAlchemy and Skype4Py. you need to install them by
easy_install or package manager.
$ sudo easy_install SQLAlchemy
$ sudo easy_install skype4py

# setup
you need to create config.py, config-sample.py is a good sample for you.

# run
firs of all, you need to launch skype client.
next, execute tiffanybot.py.

your skype might pop-up authentification window, you need to push "allow" button.
after that, enjoy bot-life!.

in default, @@@help command may be a good friend for you.
